            <abstract id="ref1" label="Abstract">These are notes of lectures and experiments made at Paris as a student at the Jardin des Plantes. The volumes are entitled: Botany &amp; Agriculture (with a large portion actually on electrical machinery); Trees and Shrubs; Chemistry, Physics, Mineralogy; and Zoology.</abstract>
